refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
boolapc_load_constants stringkey boolcase_sensitive
Carrega um conjunto de constantes do cache.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Exemplo de apc_load_constants


<?php
$constants = array(
    'ONE'   => 1,
    'TWO'   => 2,
    'THREE' => 3,
);
apc_define_constants('numbers', $constants);
apc_load_constants('numbers');
echo ONE, TWO, THREE;
?>


    &example.outputs;


123

&reftitle.seealso;
apc_define_constants define constant
Ou a referência de constantes do PHP
